OL,3,CVictims of fatal crash near Moy named
OL,5,FThe names of three people who died
OL,6,Ffollowing a road traffic collision
OL,7,Fnear Moy, County Tyrone on Saturday
OL,8,Fhave been made public.
OL,10,FThe three-vehicle crash happened on
OL,11,Fthe Armagh Road between Moy and Armagh
OL,12,Fcity on Saturday night. Emergency
OL,13,Fservices were called to the scene at
OL,14,Fabout 10.20pm.
OL,16,FConor Quinn, 31, from Derryloughan,
OL,17,FCounty Tyrone, Laura Hoy, 23, from
OL,18,FCookstown and John Guy, 48, who was
OL,19,Foriginally from Dublin but living in
OL,20,FKeady all died at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
