OL,3,CVictims of fatal crash near Moy named
OL,5,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,6,FBeck said: "At around 10.20pm, police
OL,7,Freceived a report of a three-vehicle
OL,8,Fcollision involving a red BMW, a grey
OL,9,FVolkswagen and a white Audi."Officers
OL,10,Fattended, along with colleagues from
OL,11,Fother emergency services, however, two
OL,12,Fmen, aged 31 and 48, and a woman, aged
OL,13,F23, were sadly pronounced deceased at
OL,14,Fthe scene."Four other people sustained
OL,15,Finjuries, three of whom are receiving
OL,16,Fmedical treatment."
