OL,3,CVictims of fatal crash near Moy named
OL,5,FThe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,6,F(NIAS) confirmed they received a call
OL,7,Faround half past ten on Saturday. In a
OL,8,Fstatement the NIAS said: "The Northern
OL,9,FIreland Ambulance Service received a
OL,10,F999 call at 22:23 on Saturday 21
OL,11,FFebruary, following reports of a
OL,12,Fserious Road Traffic Collision on
OL,13,FArmagh Road, Moy.
OL,15,F"NIAS dispatched 3 Rapid Response
OL,16,FParamedics, 7 Emergency Crews, 1 HART
OL,17,FCrew, an Ambulance Officer and an
OL,18,FAmbulance Doctor to the incident.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
