OL,3,CVictims of fatal crash near Moy named
OL,5,F"Following assessment and initial
OL,6,Ftreatment at the scene, 2 patients
OL,7,Fwere taken to Craigavon Area Hospital
OL,8,Fand another to Royal Victoria Hospital
OL,9,Fin Belfast."
OL,11,FPolice say inquiries are continuing
OL,12,Fand have asked anyone who was in the
OL,13,Farea and witnessed the incident to
OL,14,Fcontact them. The Armagh Road has
OL,15,Fsince reopened.
